Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I got that jerk right\Nwhere I want him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for me to end\Nthis, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Even with a hundred\Nthousand more weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,our chore boy can still\Nbring him to his knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because he does not know fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Krieg may have more\Npirates at his command,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He may have terrible weapons\Nthat cause mass destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to every thing in his path,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but he will never have\Nthat kid's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThe All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight until\Nvictory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NDon Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NCommander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When he wakes up,\Ngive him a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him that I'll\Nsee him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. It's my silly dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With this poison in my veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I may only have a\Nfew hours to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel free somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,like now, I can live those last\Nfew moments on my own terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue your dreams with every\Nlast fiber of what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will never again feel\Nlost, or hopeless, or afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned all of that\Nfrom a brave chore boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. We gratefully\Naccept this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right to assume there's\Nno need to return it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] It yours, don't\Never come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even to return this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NHe's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't you ever forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the restaurant\Nwhere the cooks fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baratie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] Hm. The cooks\Nthere sure mean business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Set Sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seafaring Cook\NSets off With Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[booming]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Waa! My hat!\NWhere's my hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOh good, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHave a good nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey... Those pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] They're gone now,\Nall thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Yeah, and Ghin asked\Nme to tell you that he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"See you on the Grand Line".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NNo, to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess I don't have to\Ndo anymore lame-o chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,since I got those pirates\Noff your back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] No, I'm not\Ngonna run away with you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some unfinished\Nbusiness here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay until Zeff\Nacknowledges my skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These bozos don't\Nknow the first thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to run a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I promised myself\Nthat one of these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It just isn't the\Nright time. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThere is one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, have you ever\Nheard of the All Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNuh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That sea is a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NIn the All Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there are fish from the\NEast Blue, the West Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the North Blue,\Nand the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That one stretch\Nof ocean has it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To us cooks, it's a\Nculinary dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A place that fantastic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has got to be on the Grand\NLine somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, where else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] The little brat\Nlooks truly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NAlright guys! Soups on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI huffs]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good, they saved\Nus some seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No chairs left for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK O laughs]\NJust sit on the floor and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no chairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NAll right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunch of jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NHey! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who prepared the\Nsoup this morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff is pretty good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I really out did myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NIs that a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely hold this\Nslop down! Bleh! Bleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I thought someone\Nlike you, would like slop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense to me, seeing\Nas, that's what pigs like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Just face it Sanji, your\Nsoup sucks. It's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleh, bleh, bleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That soup is nothing\Nshort of a delicacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong\Nwith your taste buds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! That's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NI can't eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleh, bleh! Revolting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D coughs]\NThis soup is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS murmur]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's going\Non, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sick of the\Nway you run things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a sham of a Sous Chef\Nand everybody knows it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just settle every\Nsingle little disagreement
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If the food's bad,\Nthen we're gonna say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls] What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that\Nwe're seafaring cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you'd better not waste\None single drop of that soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALl gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NBoss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That wretched little dish\Ntasted like stewed garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever served that\Nkind of trash here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd go out of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NAre you really this stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how is my\Nsoup any different
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from the stuff you make? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they're the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF growls]\NDon't flatter yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NThe Boss punched him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NHe didn't kick him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can lecture me\Non the art of cooking, do ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fat chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man who has\Ncooked on more seas
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,than days that\Nyou've been alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThat worthless old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI'm not a little brat, anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY slurps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This soup's totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us know the soup is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he's an outstanding chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here on\Nthe Baratie does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from Chef Zeff,\Nhe's the best we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D]\NThat was scary wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He seriously snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK O]\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] But that\Nthick skulled idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't listen to us if\Nwe tried to reason with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] You were saying\Nthat you needed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a cook for your ship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this isn't something I\Nwant to be asking anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but... would you mind taking\Nthat little brat along with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line is his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Boss, you sure made\Nus put on a hell of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, I was worried he\Nwas gonna figure it out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause of your bad acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Your acting was\Nway worse than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] I'm gonna get\Nsome more of that soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK O]\NYeah, that stuff is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I can hear\Neverything, Dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NSo, what do you say, Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:12:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But earlier, you mentioned you\Nneeded a cook for your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That he's suddenly not\Ngood enough for ya'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd love it if he joined\Nmy crew and came with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it seems like he\Nreally wants to stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and cook with all of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask me all you want,\Nbut I'm just not gonna take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying you\Ncan't agree to it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,until he tells you\Nhimself, s'that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! More food, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose\Nthat's fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, who knows if that\Nhardheaded little brat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,will ever agree to\Njoin up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] Yeah, Once that\Nguy makes up his mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothin' anybody\Ncan do to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMore, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? A fishman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] Did he come all the\Nway from the Fishman Islands
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--to eat here?\N-- [COOK E] You dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a human and a panshark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's Yosaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey... Big Bro Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're alone?\NWhere are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Did you find Nami?\N--[YOSAKU groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU] We never\Nactually caught up to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but, from the direction\NBig Sis is headed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we think we've figured\Nout where she's going
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and what she plans to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I see.... Then we\Ncan bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,IF our suspicions\Nturn out to be true,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then the place she intends to\Ngo could mean certain death
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of us, if we follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU] The point is, we really\Nneed your help, Big Bro Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I got it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream is foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, so's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is as good a time as any.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not start my\Nquest, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be joining\Nyour little crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,on your journey to be\NKing of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NYou hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be the\Ncook on your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, whadya' say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NThis is great, Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NWoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll get the tasty food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Are you guys\Nhappy now, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Really, I'll leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell ya' the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hopin' to\Ngive you the boot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from this restaurant personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it seems that you\Ndon't have a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with straight up abandoning us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm especially sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for making the lot of\Nyou resort to bad acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI heard everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You bunch of jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was stomping on my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the best plan that you\Ncould come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Every little thing has\Nto be a fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sick and tired of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Hmph. I never\Nhave liked children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact,\NI hate children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't a day passed\Nwhen I didn't regret
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,letting a useless little\Nbrat like you live, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Fine by me,\Nyou rotten old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the rest of\Nyour miserable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU] Whoa!\NThis is a nice ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure it's okay to use her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A] Of course!\NIt's Sanji's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK B]\NYou still need more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYup! Gonna need more meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, well how many days\Nare you gonna be out at sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NKid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm? Hey, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my logbook,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a detailed record of my one\Nyear journey to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He. He. I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Oooh- ooh! I want\Nsome more of that marbled meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough meat for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] It's the nicest sea\Nrestaurant I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHey, Sanji, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] It doesn't matter\Nwhat sort of person
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,walks through our doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they will be fed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Every starving wretch who comes\Nto us will get a fine meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nhow much we fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because we share the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI laughs]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NAre you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause we're gonna be busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] You bet! It won't be\Na problem with me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI yelps]\NOw...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZEFF grunts]\N--[SANJI yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you call peeling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThat hurt, you old fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to cook here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay outta my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and we won't have any\Nproblems! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You better watch your\Nmouth, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJ] I'm not a little brat,\Nyou crusty old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHeh! Try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Did you make\Nit all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHow is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the worst soup I've\Never had, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI whimpers]\NYou mean, old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU] Big Bro Cook\Nsure is taking his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really guys, that was just dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou don't need to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NSanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chef Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, you geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe my life to you, Old Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:21:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY whimpering]\NYou asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna miss you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll miss you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn wusses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Real men should part without\Na word, let alone tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NLet's go! Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will see you again!\NI'll come back someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOKS] Bye!\N--[PATTY] Bye, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NWe're gonna miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NGood luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] As long as you sail with\Nenough faith in yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have no fear...\Nnot even of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You will find the All Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NAll right, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Customers will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.33,0:23:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.25,0:23:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.21,0:24:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.58,0:24:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Sounds like Nami's\Nheaded to Arlong Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.83,0:24:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.67,0:24:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] It's a place over\Nrun by fishman pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NShe couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.05,0:24:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] With her looks,\Nshe might be a mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.55,0:24:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMaybe a water imp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.96,0:24:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.75,0:24:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMaybe she's half fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NNo meals for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.09,0:24:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Worst Man in\Nthe Eastern Seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.88,0:24:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Pirate Arlong!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.71,0:24:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of The Pirates!

